compress_chunk | _timescaledb_internal._hyper_1_1_chunk
-[ RECORD 2 ]--+---------------------------------------
compress_chunk | _timescaledb_internal._hyper_1_2_chunk
-[ RECORD 3 ]--+---------------------------------------
compress_chunk | _timescaledb_internal._hyper_1_3_chunk

